Package: SynergyAnalysis
Type: Package
Title: Identify Synergistic Genes from Transcriptomics Combination Treatments
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("puweilin", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "puweilin@users.noreply.github.com")
Description: R framework and Shiny app for identifying synergistic genes from
    transcriptomics data, where the combination treatment A+B produces an
    effect that exceeds the sum of A alone and B alone. Supports both a strict
    4-criteria filter (all pairwise comparisons significant + magnitude
    additivity) and a relaxed magnitude-only mode. Includes ORA enrichment
    (GO BP, KEGG) and Excel export with per-sample FPKM.
